    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-07-26T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-07-26T11:00:00-05:00" n="679"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d679">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 654.119/408</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SPA1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stovall</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berne</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-07-26T17:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1918, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received July 28, 10.18 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4090. The War Trade Board [from <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_DEL1"
                        >Dresel</persName>]:</p>
                <p>No. 105. Legation’s 4037, 22d, my 101. Cotton agreement definitely ratified by
                    Swiss Government with restriction stated my 101 and will go into force at once.
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_DEL1">Dresel</persName>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SPA1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stovall</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
